if we didn't use the word "Mama"?

58:28.560 --> 58:31.950
It makes me think of my mother
and that sort of kills it, you know?

58:32.080 --> 58:33.832
Sure.

58:39.240 --> 58:41.151
That's a boy.

58:41.280 --> 58:43.236
